I have always been passionate about using technology to connect people and broaden horizons, and I am inspired by Expedia Group's mission to power global travel for everyone, everywhere. I envision myself contributing my talent to furthering this mission by building technology that makes travel more accessible and memorable. I would love to discuss my interest in this position with your team and can be reached at #ph or #eml. Thank you for your time and consideration, I look forward to connecting!

